You want to start a franchise of an established Physical Therapy clinic. If you currently work for a bustling physical therapy practice, or you know of 1 that is open to expansion, schedule a meeting to discuss starting a franchise in another location. You can use the reputation and network that is already created, while still running your own business. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d1/Start-a-Physical-Therapy-Business-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Start-a-Physical-Therapy-Business-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/d1/Start-a-Physical-Therapy-Business-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/v4-760px-Start-a-Physical-Therapy-Business-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
